item.title: 【Unreleased/Unofficial (lossless)】FLAC - ROSALÍA - MOTOMAMI+++ (True Immersive 2.0) 16bits 44.1kHz
item.description:
True Immersive 2.0 is a stereo audio technology that I am working on to give an immersive experience mostly better and precise than Dolby Atmos and Sony 360RA. This album has its Atmos version that I published in another section of the site, but here I leave the immersive stereo version for those who want to try it only with headphones. Some songs are not present because there was not much information to extract and convert them to immersive stereo. Anyway I added 4 more songs to compensate for that. I warn you that the difference between Atmos and Trumersive is noticeable but not that much.
We give credit to the author of the stems, we have used some of them, the rest was made with AI.
